308
00:21:49.558 --> 00:21:51.268 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Üzgünüm...
-Nasıl yapabildin?

309
00:21:55.022 --> 00:21:56.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Seni kaybetmekten korktum!

310
00:21:57.274 --> 00:21:59.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yer altına döndüğünde

311
00:21:59.234 --> 00:22:00.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
her şey biter diye korktum!

312
00:22:00.444 --> 00:22:03.030 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tüm bunların, bizim sonumuz gelir diye!

313
00:22:03.113 --> 00:22:06.825 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yollarımız ayrılır diye.

314
00:22:22.632 --> 00:22:26.136 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Şimdi hatırladım!
Parçalar Vesaire dükkânı!

315
00:22:26.219 --> 00:22:28.513 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
